overview: Joshua Westover is a social entrepreneur with a passion for developing innovative products and services and is most fulfilled designing strategies and executing solutions to right the wrongs that exist in an organization or industry. Joshua’s love for people and skill for identifying mutually beneficial alliances helps open endless doors of opportunity for the EnticeLabs team. Joshua was VP of Strategy at Zinch.com before joining EnticeLabs. He graduated with honors (Magna Cum Laude) from Brigham Young University where he studied Chinese and Business.
